Change Effect

4 Field qampavg has been renamed to gain_alpha. Renaming of a field in data type may indicate a change in the semantic meaning of the field.
5 Field step_factor has been renamed to optimal_bin. Renaming of a field in data type may indicate a change in the semantic meaning of the field.
